        <mxCell id="detail4-text" value="Risk: MEDIUM | Impact: MEDIUM | Likelihood: MEDIUM&#xa;Description: New pattern, requires testing&#xa;Mitigation:&#xa;  • Test with dev cluster first&#xa;  • Validate multi-source rendering&#xa;  • Incremental rollout (one cluster at a time)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
