        <mxCell id="detail6-text" value="Risk: MEDIUM | Impact: MEDIUM | Likelihood: LOW&#xa;Description: Requires ArgoFleet to manage ArgoCD&#xa;Mitigation:&#xa;  • Verify with ArgoFleet team first&#xa;  • Document external dependency&#xa;  • Test that ArgoCD still functions&#xa;  • Clear ownership boundaries" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
