        <mxCell id="detail7-text" value="Original Risk: HIGH | Impact: HIGH | Likelihood: LOW&#xa;Description: Major security change (AVP → ESO)&#xa;Mitigation (reduces to MEDIUM):&#xa;  • ESO already in use for cluster credentials&#xa;  • Phased migration (not all at once)&#xa;  • Start with non-critical secrets&#xa;  • Parallel run during migration&#xa;  • Comprehensive secret validation&#xa;  • Rollback plan documented&#xa;Status: Risk reduced from HIGH to MEDIUM" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
